WEBVTT

00:00.201 --> 00:01.659
I didn't think you were coming.

00:03.386 --> 00:04.579
- What?
- Nothing.

00:04.659 --> 00:06.129
What the hell is that?

00:08.271 --> 00:09.232
I don't know.

00:09.459 --> 00:10.499
You okay?

00:11.248 --> 00:13.043
Gassy... Better everyday.

00:13.184 --> 00:15.248
- Could we take a break?
- Maybe a short one.

00:15.351 --> 00:17.180
This is Joanna, an old friend of mine.

00:17.349 --> 00:20.784
- How well do you know her?
- No, don't even think about it.

00:20.893 --> 00:22.161
It was that obvious, eh?

00:22.379 --> 00:24.171
Joanna and I were married for 3 years.

00:24.409 --> 00:26.415
He seems to think
that we have a lot in common.

00:26.498 --> 00:27.369
Really?

00:27.538 --> 00:28.637
I gotta go.

00:28.983 --> 00:33.516
You are gonna choose a trip to Wisconsin
over more incandescent sex with me?

00:33.605 --> 00:35.189
That was the hospital in Racine.

00:35.773 --> 00:38.734
Joanna's in quarantine there.
She's infected with CDAD.

00:38.814 --> 00:40.119
C. Difficile,

00:40.251 --> 00:43.726
just one of a whole number
of bacteria living in our intestines.

00:43.899 --> 00:46.067
Basically, your colon swells shut,

00:46.696 --> 00:48.438
eventually nothing passes through.

00:49.854 --> 00:51.527
<i>And we found where it was hiding.</i>

00:51.636 --> 00:52.775
<i>In a plant, David.</i>

00:53.014 --> 00:54.445
In the soil of a potted plant.

00:54.530 --> 00:57.790
<i>Moms. They were sold as a local
fundraiser for spina bifida research.</i>

00:58.928 --> 00:59.956
<i>David are you still there?</i>

